{"type": "article", "id": 16099, "title": "3D花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-15T06:20:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606134434Ucxle79GVtAdS0yW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这一系列的花瓶都是 3D 打印的，设计师试图用现代技术来诠释传统。经过建模、打印的步骤之后，依然使用烧制和上釉的传统手法。花瓶呈现出漂亮的渐变色，可以做出扭曲的造型，细看时还保留了线性纹路，成为具有现代感的陶瓷花瓶。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143454kgrIqRUKzQAlvTM4.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"636\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143455EHsj0wvx4Q7KiG9Y.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"636\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261434559ZQHBEVqfkI1XFzh.jpg\" width=\"584\" height=\"386\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.51059322\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143456W9UJfoE82HrujsIS.jpg\" width=\"472\" height=\"713\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.51059322\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}